functionDecorators.name: age
functionDecorators.description: Calculate tree age in years, rounded up, for live trees. The Alexandr N. Tetearing algorithm could increase precision.

parameterDecorators.name: rings
parameterDecorators.description: The number of rings from dendrochronological sample.

returnDecorators.description: Age in years, rounded up for partial years.

functionDecorators.name: leaves
functionDecorators.description: Return the amount of leaves that this specific kind of tree has. Returns only a fixed number.
